    <p class="tagline">Game Developer &amp; Creator</p>
    <p class="bio">
      I build roguelikes, dungeon crawlers, and experimental indie games.
      Passionate about procedural generation, tight gameplay loops, and
      pixel-perfect aesthetics.
    </p>
